2557
01:55:57,119 --> 01:55:58,159
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam u Donamu

2558
01:55:58,159 --> 01:56:01,119
[SPEAKER_01] i išla na misu u Brbaničevu

2559
01:56:01,119 --> 01:56:02,060
[SPEAKER_01] gdje su mi bili ovi moji

2560
01:56:02,060 --> 01:56:03,520
[SPEAKER_01] sinski i splitski pratri.

2561
01:56:03,520 --> 01:56:05,979
[SPEAKER_01] I taj unuk,

2562
01:56:05,979 --> 01:56:07,340
[SPEAKER_01] čak i taj djedica

2563
01:56:07,340 --> 01:56:09,119
[SPEAKER_01] svaki dan išao na misu

2564
01:56:09,119 --> 01:56:10,239
[SPEAKER_01] iz podvrša,

2565
01:56:10,239 --> 01:56:10,760
[SPEAKER_01] je išao,

2566
01:56:10,760 --> 01:56:12,079
