2567
01:56:12,079 --> 01:56:13,659
[SPEAKER_01] u Gospe Lurtske na misu,

2568
01:56:13,659 --> 01:56:15,640
[SPEAKER_01] a unuk je išao na druženje

2569
01:56:15,640 --> 01:56:17,359
