2573
01:56:21,380 --> 01:56:23,920
[SPEAKER_01] i tu vam je sa patron Hangom,

2574
01:56:23,920 --> 01:56:24,560
[SPEAKER_01] Marjanom,

2575
01:56:24,560 --> 01:56:26,539
[SPEAKER_01] koji su onda bili njegovi studenti,

2576
01:56:26,539 --> 01:56:27,960
[SPEAKER_01] Štajnarum koji još bio sve

2577
01:56:27,960 --> 01:56:29,420
[SPEAKER_01] i tu je bila osnovana

2578
01:56:29,420 --> 01:56:30,340
[SPEAKER_01] zajednica mladih.

2579
01:56:30,340 --> 01:56:31,439
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam došla nešto

2580
