[SPEAKER_01] kasnije je došao

2588
01:56:40,899 --> 01:56:41,819
[SPEAKER_01] Tonči Trstenjak,

2589
01:56:41,819 --> 01:56:42,659
[SPEAKER_01] Nikola Stanković,

2590
01:56:42,659 --> 01:56:43,500
[SPEAKER_01] mojte zamisliti sad,

2591
01:56:43,500 --> 01:56:44,640
[SPEAKER_01] pater Nikola Stanković

2592
01:56:47,359 --> 01:56:48,699
[SPEAKER_01] Pater Mirko Nikolić

2593
