[SPEAKER_01] one godine,

2596
01:56:52,079 --> 01:56:53,479
[SPEAKER_01] sad sam on vratio u Split.

2597
01:56:53,479 --> 01:56:55,159
[SPEAKER_01] Pa znate kako dobivate

2598
01:56:55,159 --> 01:56:56,659
[SPEAKER_01] to jedno bogatstvo

2599
01:56:56,659 --> 01:56:57,460
[SPEAKER_01] Bože rodbine,

2600
