[SPEAKER_01] sestra i majka,

2602
01:56:59,739 --> 01:57:01,140
[SPEAKER_01] one koji vrši bolju žuolju

2603
01:57:01,140 --> 01:57:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] i sad mi se ti patri ovde vrate.

2604
01:57:03,000 --> 01:57:04,779
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da je to isto

2605
01:57:04,779 --> 01:57:05,659
[SPEAKER_01] bilo jedno bogatstvo.

2606
01:57:06,119 --> 01:57:06,880
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam puno dobila

2607
01:57:06,880 --> 01:57:08,300
[SPEAKER_01] kroz te susrete,

2608
01:57:08,300 --> 01:57:10,899
[SPEAKER_01] kroz te vjeronauke,

2609
01:57:10,899 --> 01:57:11,739
[SPEAKER_01] studentske

2610
01:57:11,739 --> 01:57:13,199
[SPEAKER_01] i kroz zajednicu Jordan

2611
01:57:13,199 --> 01:57:14,699
[SPEAKER_01] koja se poslije svake godine

2612
01:57:14,699 --> 01:57:15,760
[SPEAKER_01] jedan do dva puta

2613
01:57:15,760 --> 01:57:18,060
[SPEAKER_01] Pater Hang i još neki su bili

2614
01:57:18,060 --> 01:57:19,380
[SPEAKER_01] i Salopek.

2615
01:57:19,380 --> 01:57:23,699
[SPEAKER_01] I Salopek

2616
01:57:23,699 --> 01:57:28,300
[SPEAKER_01] gospodine je isto bio u tome,

2617
01:57:28,300 --> 01:57:29,859
[SPEAKER_01] Miroslav.

2618
01:57:30,859 --> 01:57:32,739
[SPEAKER_01] Oni su bili organizatori

2619
01:57:32,739 --> 01:57:33,520
[SPEAKER_01] tih susreta.

2620
01:57:33,520 --> 01:57:34,600
[SPEAKER_01] Možete zamisliti sad,

2621
01:57:34,600 --> 01:57:36,539
[SPEAKER_01] slavimo 40 godina

2622
01:57:36,539 --> 01:57:39,100
[SPEAKER_01] od osnovana je zajednica,

2623
01:57:39,100 --> 01:57:40,399
[SPEAKER_01] tamo negdje oko 70

2624
01:57:40,399 --> 01:57:41,560
[SPEAKER_01] i znači toga ima

2625
